metadata.title: Premier Kites 9.5 Ft Wind Generator - Rainbow
description: A colorful adaptation of the large power generators seen in Europe and on windy plains in America, our version uses a unique governor arrangement to keep them turning at a constant yet mesmerizing rpm. Based on designs by Mike Delfar of Gravity Works in Franklin, Wisconsin.
